  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Here's a few pointers to help you find what you are looking for on our website:</p>
<p><br /><strong>If you are searching for a holiday,</strong> click on the holiday type you are looking for at the top of this page, then use the search facility above. Choose your departure date, travelling from and any other preferences, then click search.  You can then click into any of the accommodation listed in the results and refine your selections.</p>
<p><br /><strong>If you are looking for inspiration</strong>, Look in "Holiday Types" under each holiday type at the top of the page.</p>
<p><br /><strong>If you are searching for destination information,</strong> click on the holiday type at the top of the page, then select "Destinations" or a specific country for a list of resorts.</p>
<p><br /><strong>If you are looking for some of our best holiday offers,</strong> please refer to "Deals", at the top of the page, select a country and use the refine filters on the left of the page to narrow down your selection.</p>
<p><br /><strong>If you still can't find what you're looking for</strong>, try the <a data-udi="umb://document/0b10fcff2a594a9d9c059639f2353d29" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0b10fcff2a594a9d9c059639f2353d29}" title="Site Map">site map</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/2978da0ed64c4c85a52a04c0bf4a34eb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2978da0ed64c4c85a52a04c0bf4a34eb}" title="Frequently Asked Questions">frequently asked questions</a> section.<br /><br /><strong>Alternatively</strong>, you can <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">contact us</a>.</p>]]></bodyText>
